name: Wistia-viewer
tagline: Wistia viewer enabling HD playback, download, and social media functionality
body:
### Wistia Viewer
This viewer defaults to 1280px wide by 720px tall for watching Wistia videos in 720p HD (currently the highest supported resolution).  It also enables download and social media links, and enables the "doNotTrack" option so you aren't tracked while using this viewer.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
